headline: Genuine Parts Company to Present at the Goldman Sachs Global Retailing Conference
summary: Genuine Parts Company (NYSE: GPC), a leading global service provider of automotive and industrial replacement parts and value-added solutions, announced today that Will Stengel, President & CEO, and Bert Nappier, EVP & CFO, will present at the Goldman Sachs 32nd Annual Global Retailing Conference at 10:20 a.m. ET on Thursday, September 4, 2025.
